    },
    {
      "name": "[L2] Kitchen",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>Sersyl’s husband, Rancë, does all the cooking for the Leaky Bucket. The kitchen is Rancë’s domain. His food isn’t fancy but it is tasty, warm, and filling. Their daughter Tatril (age 15) helps him.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "_id": "hR7YoantT3IHcF0B",
