    },
    {
      "name": "[L3] Dormitory",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>The dormitory houses those who can pay for a roof over their heads but not enough for a room. Three to five guests will share the large pile of straw. The bedding is changed every month, whether it needs it or not.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "_id": "5M5hNSBHlZ1JhsUt",
