    },
    {
      "name": "[L4] Master's Rooms",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>The wealthier farmers and traders rent the master’s rooms. The inn’s best accommodation is the large room in the northwestern corner. A Khuzan trader named Haral the Stout has rented this room for the summer trading season every year since Sersyl’s mother ran the inn.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
